  <brief_title>The Effect of Stress on DNA Integrity and the Effect of Cognitive Behavioral Therapy on Stress and Infertility in Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Stress on DNA Integrity and the Effect of Cognitive Behavioral Therapy on Stress and Infertility in Women Undergoing IVF Treatment.</official_title>
