  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The general hypothesis of the research is that stress decreases fertility and that Cognitive
      Behavioral Therapy will reduce stress and increase fertility. Secondarily, we hypothesize
      that stress has a detrimental effect on DNA integrity and that stress reduction will reduce
      DNA damage in the cell.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
